@GraionDilach I restored the map lighting to Desert Rats. 

I had mistakenly thought that maps (other than  The Hot Box) could not use custom rules. I now understand that custom rules using official features, such as GlobalLightingPaletteEffect, are permitted, whilst unofficial mods such as observation posts and re-capturable oil derricks are not. 

I updated the list above with the correct UID and link for desert-rats-cnc.oramap and I updated maps.zip and maps.tar.gz: https://github.com/OpenRA/OpenRA/pull/13019#issuecomment-289580017.
